Author: Mapletyler
Text: I had this happen to me once with my bmi/weight and seeing how low I could actually go weightwise before hitting my personal "bmi limit." Was absolutely enthralled to learn that 95lbs is only 14.9 on me. I'm aaaaggges away from that and really don't want to hit it, but at the time I was excited to learn I ""could"" go double digits if I wanted.

Author: Dalos_
Text: Eating disorders turn us into monsters.
